---
title: Zucchini-and-Parmesan-Crusted Chicken with Mashed Potatoes and Green Beans
description: Topping chicken with zucchini and nutty Parmesan cheese may sound odd, but it somehow keeps the meat moist and incredibly tender in the oven. Plus, it’ll get your entire family eating more greens. When it comes to sides, our chefs chose silky mashed potatoes and green beans. After all, you can’t go wrong with the classics.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/au-zucchini-and-parmesan-topped-3242b1df.jpg
